WEBVTT

1
00:37:39.690 --> 00:37:42.380 
别当心  他弄不坏的
Don't worry. He can't hurt it.

2
00:37:42.420 --> 00:37:44.120 
嗨  你在干什么
Hey! What are you doing?

3
00:37:44.160 --> 00:37:45.620 
梦珂  把它拿回来
Meeko, bring that back!

4
00:37:45.660 --> 00:37:47.590 
不  没事  给它吧
N-No, it's all right. He can keep it.

5
00:37:47.630 --> 00:37:48.990 
就当作见面礼吧
Call it a gift.

6
00:37:51.970 --> 00:37:53.130 
那是什么
What was that?

7
00:37:53.170 --> 00:37:55.190 
-我的指南针  -指南针
-My compass. -Compass?

8
00:37:55.240 --> 00:37:57.470 
当你迷路的时候  它会告诉你怎么走
It tells you how to find your way when you get lost.

9
00:37:57.500 --> 00:37:59.470 
但是没事  回到伦敦我会买一个新的
But it's all right. I'll get another one in London.

10
00:37:59.510 --> 00:38:01.570 
伦敦  那是你的部落吗
London? Is that your village?

11
00:38:01.610 --> 00:38:03.240 
是的  一个非常大的部落
Yes. It's a very big village.

12
00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:04.800 
那是怎样的
What's it like?

13
00:38:04.850 --> 00:38:07.840 
恩  那儿有车来车往的街道
Well, it's got streets filled with carriages...

14
00:38:07.880 --> 00:38:09.470 
跨越河流的大桥
bridges over the rivers...

15
00:38:09.520 --> 00:38:12.140 
还有树一般高的建筑
and buildings as tall as trees.

